The rest of you start going in.

1676
01:50:33,335 --> 01:50:34,587
You got it.

1677
01:50:51,395 --> 01:50:52,738
Here he comes.

1678
01:51:02,990 --> 01:51:06,164
Jack. Long time no see.

1679
01:51:06,618 --> 01:51:07,961
Long time no see.

1680
01:51:08,245 --> 01:51:10,668
