let me know, all right? On me.</i>

1684
01:51:19,506 --> 01:51:20,849
That's the type of guy I am.

1685
01:51:21,008 --> 01:51:22,510
You're a real sport.

1686
01:51:22,843 --> 01:51:24,766
Just give him the disks.

1687
01:51:25,179 --> 01:51:26,681
