Why don't you just hand over the tapes,

1702
01:52:20,484 --> 01:52:21,906
we'll take a walk,
we'll go get the guy together.

1703
01:52:22,069 --> 01:52:24,071
Fuck you.
I'll see you at the arraignment.

1704
01:52:24,279 --> 01:52:26,077
