1723
01:53:42,399 --> 01:53:44,026
Take a wild guess.

1724
01:53:44,985 --> 01:53:46,862
Smoking.

1725
01:53:57,205 --> 01:53:59,833
And how will you
be paying for this, sir?

1726
01:54:08,550 --> 01:54:09,597
